message: Hello, world!
How are you?
I am doing well, thank you for asking!
What is the weather like today?
It is sunny and 75 degrees Fahrenheit.
That sounds great! I am going to go for a walk.
Have fun!
What are your plans for the weekend?
I am going to see a movie with my friends on Friday night.
That sounds like fun! What movie are you going to see?
We are going to see the new Marvel movie.
I love Marvel movies! I am excited to see the new one.
Me too!
What else are you up to this weekend?
I am going to relax and read a book.
That sounds nice. What book are you going to read?
I am going to read the new book by my favorite author.
I love that author! Their books are always so good.
I agree. I am excited to read their new book.
Well, I have to go now. It was nice talking to you!
It was nice talking to you too! Have a great weekend!
